Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.16,0:00:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs16\bord1\shad1\fscx72\fscy70\b0\i1}相对于我们居住的陆地，这是显得有些荒凉 \Nand an inhospitable place for those of us who live on land.
