Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.48,0:01:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn宋体\fs16\bord1\shad1\fscx72\fscy70\b0\i1}它们没有骨骼\NThey have no backbones,
